OL,3,CFatal mid-air paramotor crash inquiry
OL,4,Cdue to resume
OL,6,FA fatal accident inquiry into a camera
OL,7,Foperator's death following a mid-air
OL,8,Fparamotor collision is due to resume.
OL,10,FDan Burton, 54, died after his
OL,11,Fparamotor was involved in a collision
OL,12,Fwith one flown by his colleague, Sacha
OL,13,FDench, known as the "human swan", in
OL,14,Fthe Highlands in September 2021.
