OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772429722
OL,3,CFatal mid-air paramotor crash inquiry
OL,4,Cdue to resume
OL,6,FMs Dench, who survived but suffered
OL,7,Fserious injuries, was attempting a
OL,8,F3,000-mile, round Britain by paramotor
OL,9,Fchallenge to highlight climate change
OL,10,Fahead of the Cop26 conference when the
OL,11,Fincident happened near Loch Na
OL,12,FGainmhich in Sutherland.
OL,14,FShe is expected to give evidence at
OL,15,Fthe Fatal Accident Inquiry (FAI) which
OL,16,Fwill resume at Tain Sheriff Court on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,19,FThe FAI previously heard some evidence
OL,20,Fduring hearings in May last year and
OL,21,Fin January this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
